sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant PM as Actor: Program Manager
participant EVAL as Actor: Evaluator
participant STARTUP as Actor: Startup
participant BFF
participant SERVICE as Innovation Fund Service
participant DB as Primary Database
participant MQ as Event Bus

PM->BFF: Move eligible startups to fund cohort
BFF->SERVICE: Validate eligibility
SERVICE->DB: Save cohort mapping

PM->BFF: Send to DAR + assign evaluator
BFF->SERVICE: Create DAR task
SERVICE->MQ: Notify Evaluator

EVAL->BFF: Submit DAR recommendation (Yes/No)
BFF->SERVICE: Save recommendation
SERVICE->DB: Update DAR status

PM->BFF: Invite DAR-approved startups
BFF->SERVICE: Send invite
SERVICE->MQ: Notify Startup

STARTUP->BFF: Accept / Reject invite
BFF->SERVICE: Update consent status
SERVICE->DB: Persist status